{"tid":2424942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新蒲崗無牌酒吧 50多人被捕 上車人士更一度恐嚇記者","createTime":"2021-02-27T04:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T05:41:01.000Z","uid":374291,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"10f16a4537c0b116ee23ce12ed937873f1784bdc","tid":2424942,"uid":374291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"今（27日）凌晨，警方東九龍總區突襲新蒲崗大有街36號一棟工業大廈，據現場警方所指，是次行動搗破一間無牌酒吧，涉嫌無牌經營 及 違反《預防及控制疾病（業務及處所）規例》（第599F章）約五十多名男女被帶上警車離開。另外檢獲3支含有可卡因的香煙，單位內7名女子(19至29歲)亦涉嫌「管有危險藥物」被捕。<br />\n<br />\n其間一名被帶上車人士向現場多名記者恐嚇：「 影乜撚嘢！ 再影燒你報館 ！ 」<br />\n<br />\n攝:柚子，何零卒<br />\n<br />\n官方網站 : Pshk.pro<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KM2TYPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKM2TYPS.jpg&h=7d1197fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91HwLuS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91HwLuS.jpg&h=8ebc2869&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiicuWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBiicuWy.jpg&h=b58e194a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFAeJgz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFAeJgz.jpg&h=59b48e10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udVeJgz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FudVeJgz.jpg&h=8bf7eaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMpWb9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMpWb9V.jpg&h=15182333&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Of2R9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Of2R9W.jpg&h=2e63b492&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Z8oBBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Z8oBBB.jpg&h=048b35a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a6a6b91f447214342cca2f7fcfb8ba63ca2e7db","tid":2424942,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyT